Body:
Description: Dear Team,

we have not able to login via GUI, but the IP are pinging, we are facing issue to onboard the server, please try to resolve the issue.

Regards,
sai

What We've Learned Updated: managed to investigate the issue, and the cause was that the certificates could not be loaded by the nginx configuration and therefor it couldn't go through.
After I reimported the CA's and applied them to the server, the UI could be successfully open.
Next Steps Updated: have a remote session and investigate
